":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2191],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4IuP+yyN7oxdxgEAMaCDIwNjYzMjk4IOy/7NIFMAA4TUAKcgkyNjU1Nzg4MzJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"56 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-0a19d36a7a91224d02c46fc7953bd5b5_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1723151825.5519","card_id":"Q_663488472","target":{"id":663488472,"title":"我好像发现了一个统计学上的规律，有人能给出证明吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/663488472","type":"question","created":1722823925,"answer_count":14,"follower_count":173,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1291,2852,18347,29653,2340291],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"先说结论： 在均值为u，标准差为d的正态分布上进行采样，对采样结果x进行如下操作： y = d*round(x/d); 其中round(x/d)表示对x/d的值进行四舍五入取整。 操作后，得到的采样集Y的均值依然会收敛于正态分布的均值u。 背景见链接：统计学最多能跨几个数量级确定精度？ @萝卜花用python跑了一下，发现在以均值为9.1234567，方差为1的正态分布上进行采样，把采样结果进行四舍五入，得到的采样结果的均值似乎会收敛于正态分布的均值。 我在python上跑了一下，好像的确如此：from scipy import stats from half_round import half_round import numpy as np d = 1 n = 1000 offset = 1 dist = stats.norm(9.1234567,d) while offset > 0.001: measures = [ x.round() for x in dist.rvs(size=n)] #measures = [ half_round(x) for x in dist.rvs(size=n)] average = sum(measures)/len(measures) offset = abs(average - 9.1234567) print(n, average, offset) n*=10 print(\"n=\"+ str(n/10)) print(average,offset) 但是当我把标准差d改为0.5，发现采样结果四舍五入后的均值不再收敛于正态分布的均值9.1234567，结果如下所示： 我猜测是不是四舍五入以1为阶梯，与正态分布的标准差相同，所以导致采样均值之间的差别相互抵消造成的，于是引入了一个半四舍五入的函数，把四舍五入的阶梯变成了0.5：def half_round(n): # 取整数部分 integer_part = int(n) # 取小数部分 decimal_part = n - integer_part # 根据小数部分进行半四舍五入 if decimal_part < 0.25: return integer_part elif decimal_part < 0.75: return integer_part + 0.5 else: return integer_part + 1 将标准差设为0.5，然后将采样结果进行半四舍五入，得到的采样均值果然再次收敛于均值9.1234567，结果如下： 将标准差设为0.1，然后将采样结果进行半四舍五入，发现采样结果四舍五入后的均值不再收敛于正态分布的均值9.1234567，结果如下所示： 根据python跑出来的这些结果的规律，我觉得可能可以得出问题开头的那个结论，不过这毕竟是通过观察得出的结果，并不严谨，所以想知道有没有这方面的大佬来推导一下，看能否证明或者证伪这个结论？又或者这是否其实是一个已知的结论，只是我还不知道而已~"},"attached_info":"CkAIuP+yyN7oxdxgEAMaCTEwOTcxOTY4OSD16cC1BjAAOK0BQAtyCTY2MzQ4ODQ3MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"56 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6337bba29f8face173b1dd5ddd576ac8_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1723151825.7457","card_id":"Q_663796870","target":{"id":663796870,"title":"如何评价漫画《一人之下》第681（725）话？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/663796870","type":"question","created":1723133645,"answer_count":21,"follower_count":19,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[125,169573,225101,394722,3498261],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IuP+yyN7oxdxgEAMaCTEwOTc4ODA5MCDN3dO1BjAAOBNADHIJNjYzNzk2ODcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"55 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1723151825.7670","card_id":"Q_663710964","target":{"id":663710964,"title":"享界S9上市24小时大定超2500台，对于这个成绩你如何看待？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/663710964","type":"question","created":1723045799,"answer_count":66,"follower_count":93,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5263,3358807],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"据鸿蒙智行官方消息，品牌首款纯电旗舰行政轿车享界S9上市24小时大定超2500台。 相比于另一款旗舰问界M9，享界S9的大定确实差点意思，不过考虑到它是一台40多万的纯电轿车，在横向对比同价位竞品后，这2500台的大定又有着不错的含金量。 目前享界S9已经开启交付，余承东现身并为首批车主交付新车，确实做到了上市即交付，至于后续订单量如何，还有待进一步验证，这个周末过后应该会有答案。 华